    p I love to create visual programs such as fractal generators, simulations, games, and anything else I come up with.
    p
      | My other hobbies include hiking, cooking, and playing
      a(href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Go_(game)" target="_blank" rel="noopener")  Go.
    p
